title: Sage Francis - Copper Gone (2014) EXPLICIT
description:
SAGE FRANCIS...relocked and reloaded.

After a 4-year hiatus, Sage Francis has returned with his new album "COPPER GONE", is available now here from STRANGE FAMOUS RECORDS. It features beat production from long-time music affiliates BUCK 65, ALIAS, CECIL OTTER, REANIMATOR, and more.
